Class Cell

  • java.lang.Object
    • at.ac.univie.swe2.SS2017.team403.Cell
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable

    public class Cell
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Externalizable
    This class is used to handle all operations connected to a Cell. A cell-object is part of a worksheet and contains either a cellValue which is also an object or a formula.
